<p>Stewart Brand writes of the three most popular cars ever made:</p><blockquote><p>THE THREE MOST POPULAR CARS ever made have this in common: they were cheap, they retained their basic design for decades, and they invited repair by the owner.  The Ford Model T sold 16.5 million between 1908 and 1927.  The Volkswagen Beetle sold 21.5 million between 1938 and 2003.  The Lada Classic from Russia sold 18 million between 1970 and 2012.<sup>1</sup> </p></blockquote><p>In essence, they were easy to maintain. Read the piece <a href="https://books.worksinprogress.co/book/maintenance-of-everything/vehicles/what-the-three-most-popular-cars-in-history-have-in-common/1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">here</a>. Comment on the piece <a href="https://books.worksinprogress.co/book/maintenance-of-everything/vehicles/what-the-three-most-popular-cars-in-history-have-in-common/1?mode=suggest" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">here</a>. </p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff9559a4d-3e89-4dd4-805c-f5c14e9097ff_1647x1098.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux. 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux. 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/D2udgjbMvKLI2RV3KhP1xEjGKz_ 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/oOl_gQCdlp6-" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/xz9L_Ssan_ 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/ZJyPZtHt8V-9Li06pV0jg6PlHfd56lV_3l1jk4cI7XQ=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZmOTU1OWE0ZC0zZTg5LTRkZDQtODA1Yy1mNWMxNGU5MDk3ZmZfMTY0N3gxMDk4L